	* sbin/route/route.c (freebsd[23], netbsd, bsdi[34]):
	  use scoped address notation when printing IPv6 link-local multicast
	  addresses.

2000-04-20  JINMEI, Tatuya  <jinmei@isl.rdc.toshiba.co.jp>
